      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           sort      srt                  on   ascending srt-key
                     input  procedure     is   scr-mov-fil-inp-000
                                          thru scr-mov-fil-inp-999
                     output procedure     is   scr-mov-fil-out-000
                                          thru scr-mov-fil-out-999    .
