      *                  * Aggiornamento record [sct]                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   agg-rec-sct-000      thru agg-rec-sct-999        .
       scr-mov-fil-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Scrittura movimento su file : Input procedure per sort    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       scr-mov-fil-inp-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Start su righe corpo                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "ST"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      1                    to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
