      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           release   srt-rec                                          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo su lettura catena                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     scr-mov-fil-inp-100.
       scr-mov-fil-inp-999.
           exit.

